articles.title: Supreme Court preserves key part of Obamacare coverage requirements - AP News
articles.description: The Supreme Court has preserved a key part of the Affordable Care Act’s preventive health care coverage requirements, rejecting a challenge from Christian employers to the provision that affects 150 million Americans. Friday's ruling comes in a Texas case ove…
articles.content: The Supreme Court is seen on Capitol Hill in Washington, Dec. 17, 2024. (AP Photo/J. Scott Applewhite, File)
